    "body": ">  is this possible?\n\nThis is not possible using the `globalShortcut` APIs. Electron wraps Chrome's [global_shortcut_listener.h](https://cs.chromium.org/chromium/src/chrome/browser/extensions/global_shortcut_listener.h) API which only exposes a key press event.\n\nYou could write a native module that hooks into OS keyboard APIs and implement this that way for your app. Closing this out.\n"
